PrecisAppointment of HUGUETTE LABELLE, of Gloucester, Ontario, LEWIS PERINBAM, of Vancouver, British Columbia, and LUCILLE COLLETTE, of Moncton, New Brunswick, not employed in the Public Service, to be governors of the Canadian Centre for Management Development, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
